name: The Keys to Love by SouloSaint

metadata.name: Infatuation at First Sight #1/5
metadata.description:
When you first meet and fall in love with someone the feelings that rush through your mind can never be fully described with words. The joy and excitement of the honeymoon phase is everything you love about love.

Whether it be the butterflies you get from being around this person or all the new experiences you're having with them. Everything you do with this person brings you a warmth that only the sun can match.
